Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has finally calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he out of his mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing terrorists isn't our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the Secrets before a fusion explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the mission of IFO teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any spare time to take on extra tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That much should be enough for him, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unprecedented, but we're considering something serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a verbal warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even a punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't forget about what happened with team Goldilocks either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll trust you and we won't persecute this any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IFO pilots are like my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A father should trust his children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, miss, give me a large cup of hot generation coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that supposed to be threatening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you keeping Ao under surveillance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more discrete about it. It's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been ordered to do it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting pressure on him by being obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something you guys could come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president's orders, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're not getting along well with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a big fan of his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received an official request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're to mobilize immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faisal Arabia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It showed up at a troublesome spot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Allied Forces is contacting you, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it in my office. Forward it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost a team in Columbia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there was a terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're piling up losses, Cristophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the trouble caused, Secretary of State.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to think of what's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Nirvash of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the senators are complaining that it's the lost Mark I,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was built with our precious tax dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are trying to pressure the President by using the mass media.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's election season. They won't be picky with methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Nirvash and the Mark I are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will the US government believe what you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Faisal Arabia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still quite far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we prioritize Quartz recovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what would we do if the enemy accelerated?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment the Secret showed up, our possible courses of action became limited to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:08:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so they were tailing me by the President's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he went on about fatherly trust and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't mean what he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he said that to you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IFO pilots are like my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a good idea to say that in front of his daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur is the President's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've confirmed the Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Secret is very similar to the one spotted in 1752 in Philadelphia, America.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, lightning caused serious \Ndamages to places the Secret passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phenomenon we call "lightning" is the result of the difference in ionic charge exceeding a certain—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation is cancelled. The Triton is to return immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President? What kind of an order is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the ship around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made some sort of deal in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, the only one who can put \Npressure on the President is the US government.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would America...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faisal Arabia, the location where the Scub appeared, is the most prominent anti-US country in the Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America, on the other hand, antagonized Faisal Arabia as a supporter of terrorism,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making the two countries being constantly on the verge of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the background of Faisal Arabia's anti-US \Nposition is the internal opposition of royal—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a fusion explosion occurred, it would seriously damage the enemy country,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and, at the same time, prevent the establishment of a plant coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the President agree to such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal must somehow be beneficial to the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! The President must be—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling us to turn back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is telling us to watch them all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elopement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same, right, Ao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from Gazelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're similar, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you work for your father's company if you hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago, Maman and I got into a traffic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one of us donated our internal organs to the other, the other could survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the doctors told my father that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he chose me... and killed Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had made the other choice back then, Maman would still be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my father for making me live with this burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I do what annoys him the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us take a look at inside Faisal Arabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are footages of the Abuha region where the G-Monster first appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The governments of Britain, France, China and other countries
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the Triton immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}have voiced intent of immediate aid to the stricken country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing these footages, the public \Ndemanded that Faisal Arabia must be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Allied Forces had no choice but to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our return order was revoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are resuming the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't have it their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show it to America and our stupid President!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stupid President"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a complete victory, right, Miss Fleur?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two should gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,180 seconds until we reach the combat area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got visual on the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting it on screen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lightning is merely a side effect of the \Nexpulsion of ionized particles from the Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Secret normally doesn't attack IFOs as the trapar field shields them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the lightning is an electric discharge \Nindependent of the Secret's intent, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lightning can strike outside of the ZOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The IFOs are equipped with electricity \Ndischarge shields for immediate protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you get hit directly, the lightning may cause system errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just telling us to be careful, but what exactly are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes it sound so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your complaints back in the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're outside of the Zone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hot day in Little Russia...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of charged particles is increasing by 250% per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The charged area is likewise growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elena, respond! Elena!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash and Alleluia, wait for my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our strategy won't work without Kyrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, the Secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret has emitted all charged particles it had stored up, and has started lifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is expected to stop in 75 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A drop is expected. The destination of its trajectory is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Scub Coral!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going for a direct impact?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation cancelled! Return immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed. We can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lose if we retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fleur! Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, come back! Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-minus 115 seconds until fusion explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fleur, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alleluia is too lightly armed for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely cannot lose this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Secret has reached 7500 feet above Faisal Arabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has lost its thrust and is beginning its descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my father too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't risk my life for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay alive no matter what and give him a good beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mustn't die either, Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Fleur.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvash and Alleliua have reached the Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-minus 25 seconds until fusion explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, nine, eight, seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,six, five, four, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Georg, how's Alleluia and Nirvash?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alleluia and Nirvash are both intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life signals have been detected, so it is safe to assume the pilots are unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you two going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see the stupid President.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must report our victory to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what face he's making...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the Americans spanked him and he's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the stupid President going to welcome us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Don't pull so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look who we've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! We look awesome, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you have left your designated locations without permission during an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we broadcasted that video,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there were immediate reports that we're not there despite an official request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Americans called of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought we're the source of such reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I told them I didn't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did you stay despite receiving the return order?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engine troubles. We had some difficulties fixing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President was behind those footages...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lied to the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were able to go back because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saved lots of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleur, did we really win?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, when did you start dropping the "Miss"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man wishing for change to create something new summons melancholic memories from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.45,0:24:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the one from the jet black depth offer to the man,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.55,0:24:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what does it show to the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka Seven AO, episode nine: In The Dark We Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
